00:03:14.862 --> 00:03:17.960
then the derivative, f prime of x,

00:03:17.960 --> 00:03:20.247
and this is something that you
will see in your textbooks.

00:03:20.247 --> 00:03:21.541
Well, this is going to be

00:03:21.541 --> 00:03:24.490
